drv
Script emos_testset_driver

MainTest
  |
  +--emos_testset_driver

A simple driver for a single test set. This driver was designed to be used with TestDirector. The idea is that we could create test sets in TestDirector and replace with them the Frameworks concept of "test suite". So a test set in TestDirector could act a counterpart of one test suite. What we need to do is create automate tests within the test subject tree that all prepare the required three parameters and call this test.
